    "body": "Thanks @jrainville I've worked up a new option where we show a banner (floating or pinned) on the `All members` view which is interactive - on click it displays a dialog of all members that are yet to rejoin via the new community control node.\r\n\r\nI think this works well because it avoids us adding another tab, it also avoids us placing these users in the `Pending` tab which is not technically the right place for them and also allows for the segregation of true members and those that are yet to rejoin. The owner also has the option to remove this info from the UI in the event there are a few stragglers that take weeks to rejoin or if they are simply not interested in this metric.\r\n\r\nLet me know what you think and we can take a look with John when he returns :)\r\n\r\nFloating banner variant:\r\nhttps://www.figma.com/file/qHfFm7C9LwtXpfdbxssCK3/Kuba%E2%8E%9CDesktop---Communities?type=design&node-id=44434-265983&mode=design&t=J5xdI3aZ5Gmmi8Ew-4\r\n\r\nPinned banner variant:\r\nhttps://www.figma.com/file/qHfFm7C9LwtXpfdbxssCK3/Kuba%E2%8E%9CDesktop---Communities?type=design&node-id=44434-236532&mode=design&t=J5xdI3aZ5Gmmi8Ew-4",
